Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:12.00,Ref,,0,0,0,,And not that my parents are the best example, but I mean, they dated for four weeks and they were married for 23, 24 years. So it's like I don't feel like I have to date you for X amount of years before I ask you to marry me. I think in the amount of time that we were together, I knew through all of our experiences together that this is what I want for the rest of my life.
